        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Recently I bought &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;simondev.io&#x2F;about&quot;&gt;Simon&#x27;s&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; course on &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;simondev.io&#x2F;lessons&#x2F;math&quot;&gt;Math for Game Developers&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; and as I finally found some time to go through the first couple of  chapters I would like to share my lecture notes here.
I used Racket for mathematical functions and comments for plain English, a lot of stuff is also borrowed from the wiki page on &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;en.wikipedia.org&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Euclidean_vector&quot;&gt;Euclidean vectors&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</summary>
        
